# Parchment API

Programmatically manage your collections, pages, and blocks.

## Base URL
https://ouhjptbfjanipaljcadf.supabase.co/functions/v1/api

## Authentication
All requests require header: x-api-key

## Permissions
- can_read_pages
- can_create_collections
- can_delete_collections
- can_create_pages
- can_delete_pages
- can_write_blocks

## Rate limits
- 60 requests/minute per API key
- 1000 requests/day per API key
- 10KB max block content

## Actions
- list_collections
- create_collection
- delete_collection
- list_pages
- create_page
- delete_page
- get_page
- update_blocks
- delete_block

## delete_block example
curl -X POST https://ouhjptbfjanipaljcadf.supabase.co/functions/v1/api \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "x-api-key: pmt_your_key" \
  -d '{"action":"delete_block","page_id":"<page_id>","block_id":"<block_id>"}'

## Error codes
- 400 bad request / unknown action
- 401 missing or invalid API key
- 403 permission denied
- 404 resource not found
- 413 block too large (>10KB)
- 429 rate limit exceeded
- 500 internal server error
